{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, OTFS is considered an effective enabler for ISAC due to its advantages of high spectrum efficiency, high design flexibility, and low PAPR.",
    "Therefore, great efforts have been made to realize the potential of OTFSenabled ISAC.",
    "For example, Raviteja et al. [168] first used OTFS for target detection, demonstrating its superiority over OFDM.",
    "Gaudio et al. [106] showed that the OTFS can provide the near-optimal radar sensing performance and outperform the OFDM in the achievable communication rate, making it more suitable for joint target sensing and communication.",
    "Yuan et al. [108] investigated the OTFS-based ISAC for vehicular systems, where the roadside units transmit the OTFS waveform for both vehicle sensing and downlink communication."
  ]
}